dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This is a points dataset showing the locations of all archaeological monuments recorded in the Northern Ireland Sites and Monuments Record. Please note this data has a zoom extent of 120,000.

The resouce was created using grid refences obtained from OS 6 inch maps to place a point at the centre of each recorded archaeological site
